summary: How long have you known this existence, Vince?

summary: Males of the Roserade line typically have larger and much more vibrant flowers than their female counterparts, so they are much...
body: Males of the Roserade line typically have larger and much more vibrant flowers than their female counterparts, so they are much more commonly used in contests. The healthier the Pokémon is, the more their flowers grow, and the stronger the poison within them is.
